You're such a pretty young lady.

00:05:12.896 --> 00:05:13.813 position:50% align:center
Thanks.

00:05:13.897 --> 00:05:14.564 position:50% align:center
Ai's Mom!

00:05:14.647 --> 00:05:16.066 position:50% align:center
Can we get some cake?

00:05:16.149 --> 00:05:17.901 position:50% align:center
Oh, and lay out
Neiru's snacks, too.

00:05:17.984 --> 00:05:19.361 position:50% align:center
