Of course.

00:05:19.444 --> 00:05:22.530 position:50% align:center
You have so many
friends now, don't you?

00:05:22.614 --> 00:05:25.742 position:50% align:center
That's wonderful! Right, Ai?

00:05:25.825 --> 00:05:27.118 position:50% align:center
Mom!

00:05:27.202 --> 00:05:29.537 position:50% align:center
Pretty, pretty, pretty please!

00:05:29.621 --> 00:05:31.915 position:50% align:center
Ugh! Do you really
have no shame?

00:05:31.998 --> 00:05:34.125 position:50% align:center
You haven't even
finished yours yet.

00:05:34.209 --> 00:05:35.001 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Stingy.

00:05:35.085 --> 00:05:36.503 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
Now, now.

00:05:36.586 --> 00:05:40.006 position:50% align:center
Anyway, are you really a student
at my uncle's school, Ai?

00:05:40.090 --> 00:05:41.383 position:50% align:center
He's so hot.

00:05:41.466 --> 00:05:43.468 position:50% align:center
I hear he's real popular
with all the girls there.

00:05:43.551 --> 00:05:45.053 position:50% align:center
