Who's Koito?

00:05:53.228 --> 00:05:56.189 position:50% align:center
The girl that
Ai's trying to save.

00:05:56.272 --> 00:05:57.524 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
Oh, I see.

00:05:58.775 --> 00:05:59.693 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Huh.

00:05:59.776 --> 00:06:01.569 position:50% align:center
I just had a crazy thought.

00:06:01.653 --> 00:06:03.363 position:50% align:center
Well, are you gonna share it?

00:06:07.492 --> 00:06:09.035 position:50% align:center
Okay, check it out.

00:06:09.119 --> 00:06:10.620 position:50% align:center
Maybe Ai's best friend, Koito,

00:06:10.704 --> 00:06:13.665 position:50% align:center
