dating Mister Sawaki.

00:06:13.748 --> 00:06:15.667 position:50% align:center
Then, something terrible
happened, and that's why she--

00:06:15.750 --> 00:06:17.752 position:50% align:center
[doorbell rings]

00:06:17.836 --> 00:06:20.088 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI] Oh. Sorry.
Do you have company?

00:06:20.171 --> 00:06:22.424 position:50% align:center
--[TAE] We do, but it's fine.
--[MOMOE] Whoa! Wait a minute!

00:06:22.507 --> 00:06:24.384 position:50% align:center
My uncle is not like that.

00:06:24.467 --> 00:06:27.095 position:50% align:center
He's probably the sweetest
guy in the whole world.

00:06:27.178 --> 00:06:29.222 position:50% align:center
He rescues a ton of cats!

00:06:29.305 --> 00:06:32.225 position:50% align:center
[RIKA] Maybe he's the dude
version of a crazy cat lady.

00:06:32.308 --> 00:06:34.477 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU] You'd be surprised
who has a dark side.

00:06:34.561 --> 00:06:36.271 position:50% align:center
For real!

00:06:36.354 --> 00:06:38.398 position:50% align:center
So, a teacher got
handsy with a student...

00:06:38.481 --> 00:06:40.692 position:50% align:center
...and when things
got sketch, bam!

00:06:40.775 --> 00:06:42.485 position:50% align:center
He drops her.

00:06:42.569 --> 00:06:43.903 position:50% align:center
He's not like that!

00:06:43.987 --> 00:06:45.196 position:50% align:center
Maybe she got knocked up.

00:06:45.280 --> 00:06:46.156 position:50% align:center
What?

00:06:46.239 --> 00:06:47.157 position:50% align:center
Pregnant.

00:06:47.240 --> 00:06:49.951 position:50% align:center
Yeah, scandalous!

00:06:50.035 --> 00:06:51.995 position:50% align:center
Just give it a rest!

00:06:53.538 --> 00:06:55.498 position:50% align:center
Uh. Sorry.

00:06:55.582 --> 00:06:58.126 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
I was messing around, jeez.

00:06:58.209 --> 00:06:59.544 position:50% align:center
I didn't mean it!

00:07:01.254 --> 00:07:04.466 position:50% align:center
Well, anyway,
I don't know why Koito died.

00:07:04.549 --> 00:07:06.843 position:50% align:center
I really wish I did, though.

00:07:06.926 --> 00:07:08.053 position:50% align:center
You know?

00:07:11.181 --> 00:07:13.516 position:50% align:center
