00:07:21.775 --> 00:07:24.986 position:50% align:center
to see if you've got proof of
his little indiscretion!

00:07:25.070 --> 00:07:27.655 position:50% align:center
That makes sense,
though, doesn't it?

00:07:27.739 --> 00:07:29.199 position:50% align:center
[AI]
I can't ask her.

00:07:29.282 --> 00:07:31.910 position:50% align:center
My mom really
trusts Mister Sawaki,

00:07:31.993 --> 00:07:34.454 position:50% align:center
and I'm always making
her worry as it is.

00:07:34.537 --> 00:07:35.830 position:50% align:center
But it's weird, though.

00:07:35.914 --> 00:07:37.290 position:50% align:center
She stopped asking
about my injuries

00:07:37.374 --> 00:07:39.876 position:50% align:center
when I clammed up about 'em.

00:07:39.959 --> 00:07:41.961 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Clammed up, huh?

00:07:42.045 --> 00:07:44.339 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU chuckles]

00:07:44.422 --> 00:07:45.965 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Hold on--?

00:07:46.049 --> 00:07:47.717 position:50% align:center
