00:07:47.801 --> 00:07:50.178 position:50% align:center
It's funny.
I can just picture it.

00:07:50.261 --> 00:07:51.554 position:50% align:center
Ai as a little clam.

00:07:51.638 --> 00:07:54.391 position:50% align:center
Uh! Hey! Come on!

00:07:54.474 --> 00:07:56.142 position:50% align:center
Pro tip: Don't tell
her your injures came

00:07:56.226 --> 00:07:58.228 position:50% align:center
