you were on something.

00:08:02.399 --> 00:08:04.901 position:50% align:center
That, or she
wouldn't believe you.

00:08:04.984 --> 00:08:06.236 position:50% align:center
Indeed.

00:08:06.319 --> 00:08:08.780 position:50% align:center
That's why we can't
tell anyone what we do.

00:08:08.863 --> 00:08:10.365 position:50% align:center
It's our little secret.

00:08:10.448 --> 00:08:12.909 position:50% align:center
A whole world that
no one else knows about.

00:08:12.992 --> 00:08:14.160 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:08:14.244 --> 00:08:18.081 position:50% align:center
A whole world that...
no one else knows about.

00:08:19.374 --> 00:08:20.834 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI]
Momoe's here?

00:08:20.917 --> 00:08:23.920 position:50% align:center
