because she looks just like you.

00:08:24.004 --> 00:08:25.588 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI]
They go to different schools.

00:08:25.672 --> 00:08:27.340 position:50% align:center
Where did they meet?

00:08:30.719 --> 00:08:33.346 position:50% align:center
