to have a complex about it.

00:08:33.430 --> 00:08:35.974 position:50% align:center
Your eyes are charming. Unique.

00:08:36.057 --> 00:08:37.517 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Okay.

00:08:37.600 --> 00:08:40.687 position:50% align:center
[SAWAKI] I'm going to paint
you exactly how I see you.

00:08:40.770 --> 00:08:42.105 position:50% align:center
