00:08:51.281 --> 00:08:53.283 position:50% align:center
He says he wants to win a prize,

00:08:53.366 --> 00:08:56.202 position:50% align:center
so he can make
a living as a painter.

00:08:56.286 --> 00:08:57.746 position:50% align:center
[AI]
A painting of me?

00:08:57.829 --> 00:08:59.497 position:50% align:center
[KOITO]
Have confidence.

00:08:59.581 --> 00:09:02.083 position:50% align:center
If you can't, then maybe
you should decline.

00:09:02.167 --> 00:09:05.462 position:50% align:center
Mister Sawaki's
future is on the line.

00:09:05.545 --> 00:09:06.880 position:50% align:center
[AI]
I just...

00:09:15.889 --> 00:09:18.975 position:50% align:center
[RIKA] You know, I wish my mom
were more like yours, Ai.

00:09:19.059 --> 00:09:19.893 position:50% align:center
