to be a parent.

00:09:32.864 --> 00:09:34.574 position:50% align:center
No wonder I'm screwed up.

00:09:35.116 --> 00:09:36.201 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
It's your turn, Rika.

00:09:36.284 --> 00:09:37.160 position:50% align:center
I'm lucky.

00:09:37.243 --> 00:09:38.411 position:50% align:center
I don't know how,

00:09:38.495 --> 00:09:40.080 position:50% align:center
