[RIKA]
Because it's your turn, duh.

00:09:58.014 --> 00:10:00.767 position:50% align:center
That attitude belongs
in the fifties, fool.

00:10:00.850 --> 00:10:02.102 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Who you callin' "fool," fool?

00:10:02.185 --> 00:10:04.646 position:50% align:center
