00:10:33.258 --> 00:10:34.884 position:50% align:center
But I want to be free.

00:10:34.968 --> 00:10:37.887 position:50% align:center
You wouldn't tie me down, right?

00:10:37.971 --> 00:10:39.597 position:50% align:center
Oh, whatever.

00:10:39.681 --> 00:10:42.642 position:50% align:center
Hey, look at my hair,
isn't it pretty?

00:10:42.726 --> 00:10:44.936 position:50% align:center
Not a single split
end to be found.

00:10:45.020 --> 00:10:46.855 position:50% align:center
I'm at my prettiest right now.

00:10:46.938 --> 00:10:48.982 position:50% align:center
Nothing can replace
youth in that regard.

00:10:49.065 --> 00:10:50.233 position:50% align:center
I don't care.

00:10:50.316 --> 00:10:51.943 position:50% align:center
Aren't you going to ask me?

00:10:52.027 --> 00:10:55.447 position:50% align:center
You must be curious
about why I died.

00:10:55.530 --> 00:10:57.824 position:50% align:center
I'm just here to
complete my objective.

00:10:58.992 --> 00:11:00.201 position:50% align:center
Get back!

00:11:05.999 --> 00:11:08.376 position:50% align:center
Girls grow up into women.

