It's a miraculous thing,
much like a butterfly emerging.

00:11:12.213 --> 00:11:13.673 position:50% align:center
One, brief moment.

00:11:13.757 --> 00:11:16.051 position:50% align:center
A fleeting glimpse
of shocking beauty.

00:11:16.134 --> 00:11:17.635 position:50% align:center
