this girl was your friend.

00:14:20.068 --> 00:14:23.738 position:50% align:center
Yeah, I got full-body chills
and started shaking all over!

00:14:23.822 --> 00:14:26.825 position:50% align:center
What was I supposed to do?

00:14:31.246 --> 00:14:34.082 position:50% align:center
