Well, that's enough gloomy talk.

00:14:34.165 --> 00:14:36.126 position:50% align:center
There are lots of
other games in this place.

00:14:36.209 --> 00:14:38.128 position:50% align:center
Let's try 'em all out!

00:14:38.211 --> 00:14:39.671 position:50% align:center
