00:14:57.897 --> 00:14:59.482 position:50% align:center
That's my philosophy.

00:15:01.735 --> 00:15:04.362 position:50% align:center
Ooh, hey, what's that one, Ai?

00:15:09.617 --> 00:15:12.495 position:50% align:center
