That was a first for me.

00:15:37.562 --> 00:15:38.813 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Yeah, same here.

00:15:40.899 --> 00:15:42.192 position:50% align:center
[ACCA]
You've had your fun.

00:15:42.275 --> 00:15:43.526 position:50% align:center
Now, buy your Eggs.

00:15:43.610 --> 00:15:46.529 position:50% align:center
Then go home and
get some sleep, kids.

00:15:46.613 --> 00:15:48.615 position:50% align:center
But I don't wanna leave.

00:15:48.698 --> 00:15:52.035 position:50% align:center
I'm having the time
of my life in this place.

00:15:52.118 --> 00:15:53.620 position:50% align:center
[groans]

00:15:53.703 --> 00:15:55.830 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE] Been a while
since I've had this much fun.

00:15:55.914 --> 00:15:57.374 position:50% align:center
Oh, good grief.

00:15:57.457 --> 00:15:59.501 position:50% align:center
This is your fault
for spoiling them.

00:15:59.584 --> 00:16:02.962 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE] Oh hey, Neiru,
can I have your contact info?

00:16:03.046 --> 00:16:03.797 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
Yeah.

00:16:03.880 --> 00:16:05.340 position:50% align:center
Will you tell me yours, too?

00:16:05.423 --> 00:16:07.133 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
Of course. One sec.

00:16:07.217 --> 00:16:08.134 position:50% align:center
Here ya go.

00:16:08.218 --> 00:16:09.719 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA]
You're too uptight.

00:16:09.803 --> 00:16:12.138 position:50% align:center
What if we just didn't buy Eggs?

00:16:12.222 --> 00:16:13.264 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:16:13.348 --> 00:16:14.391 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Now I think about it,

00:16:14.474 --> 00:16:17.352 position:50% align:center
