to take responsibility

00:16:22.899 --> 00:16:25.568 position:50% align:center
for her bad decision
to kill herself?

00:16:25.652 --> 00:16:26.528 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
Really?

00:16:26.611 --> 00:16:28.655 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Well, am I wrong?

00:16:28.738 --> 00:16:31.032 position:50% align:center
I knew it.
It's all an act, you are cruel.

00:16:31.116 --> 00:16:34.577 position:50% align:center
No! I'm a woman,
so, sometimes I get swept up

00:16:34.661 --> 00:16:36.329 position:50% align:center
in the moment by my feelings.

00:16:36.413 --> 00:16:37.664 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
Oh, come on.

00:16:37.747 --> 00:16:40.583 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
What about you, Momoe?

00:16:40.667 --> 00:16:42.919 position:50% align:center
Are you responsible?

00:16:43.003 --> 00:16:44.629 position:50% align:center
I mean, sure, you feel guilty.

00:16:44.713 --> 00:16:46.006 position:50% align:center
I feel the same way.

00:16:46.089 --> 00:16:47.882 position:50% align:center
But, still,
should we really take

00:16:47.966 --> 00:16:49.634 position:50% align:center
full responsibility like this?

00:16:49.718 --> 00:16:53.471 position:50% align:center
To the point that we'd risk
our own lives over it?

00:16:53.555 --> 00:16:55.807 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
I don't know.

00:16:55.890 --> 00:16:57.726 position:50% align:center
Rika.

00:16:58.727 --> 00:17:00.979 position:50% align:center
I think that's enough.

00:17:01.062 --> 00:17:02.772 position:50% align:center
Especially, you, Ai.

00:17:02.856 --> 00:17:05.650 position:50% align:center
