00:17:28.757 --> 00:17:32.677 position:50% align:center
if Koito wants to come back
to life in the first place!

00:17:32.761 --> 00:17:33.845 position:50% align:center
That's not...

00:17:33.928 --> 00:17:35.847 position:50% align:center
What, did Koito's
stupid statue tell you

00:17:35.930 --> 00:17:38.850 position:50% align:center
that she wants to come back?

00:17:38.933 --> 00:17:40.435 position:50% align:center
