something like that?

00:17:40.518 --> 00:17:41.478 position:50% align:center
[MOMOE]
Rika, stop it, for real.

00:17:41.561 --> 00:17:43.229 position:50% align:center
Someone has to be the bad guy!

00:17:43.313 --> 00:17:45.940 position:50% align:center
