00:17:53.740 --> 00:17:55.950 position:50% align:center
For someone selfish enough to--

00:17:56.034 --> 00:17:58.078 position:50% align:center
Selfish enough
to kill themselves?

00:17:58.161 --> 00:18:00.830 position:50% align:center
