to save her sister.

00:18:00.914 --> 00:18:02.582 position:50% align:center
You're wrong.

00:18:02.665 --> 00:18:05.335 position:50% align:center
[RIKA]
Wrong about what?

00:18:05.418 --> 00:18:07.087 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
My sister stabbed me.

00:18:07.170 --> 00:18:08.630 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Huh?

00:18:08.713 --> 00:18:11.675 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU] Then, she ran away
and jumped off a bridge.

00:18:11.758 --> 00:18:13.468 position:50% align:center
[AI]
Stabbed you?

00:18:13.551 --> 00:18:16.888 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU] That's what they told
me when I woke up in the ICU.

00:18:16.971 --> 00:18:19.516 position:50% align:center
[RIKA] Then you've got
even less of a reason.

00:18:19.599 --> 00:18:23.186 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU] The scar aches
and keeps me awake at night.

00:18:23.269 --> 00:18:24.729 position:50% align:center
Or, it did.

00:18:24.813 --> 00:18:27.899 position:50% align:center
But the pain has faded a little
since I started coming here.

00:18:29.943 --> 00:18:31.486 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
When I try to forget her,

00:18:31.569 --> 00:18:35.532 position:50% align:center
my scar aches, like a curse.

00:18:35.615 --> 00:18:38.284 position:50% align:center
That's why I go.

00:18:38.368 --> 00:18:41.955 position:50% align:center
No other reason.

00:18:42.038 --> 00:18:43.623 position:50% align:center
It's for me.

00:18:47.919 --> 00:18:50.922 position:50% align:center
[URA-ACCA] None of you have
to go if you don't want to.

00:18:51.006 --> 00:18:53.133 position:50% align:center
Guilt and curiosity fade.

00:18:53.216 --> 00:18:55.552 position:50% align:center
Sooner or later,
you'll forget about them.

00:18:55.635 --> 00:18:56.970 position:50% align:center
It's okay.

00:18:57.053 --> 00:18:58.888 position:50% align:center
You don't have to go.

00:18:58.972 --> 00:19:00.890 position:50% align:center
You understand?

00:19:00.974 --> 00:19:03.059 position:50% align:center
I mean, after all.

00:19:03.143 --> 00:19:05.186 position:50% align:center
That's just adolescence, right?

00:19:08.815 --> 00:19:12.193 position:50% align:center
[AOI] Beauty is only a momentary
season of metamorphosis.

00:19:12.277 --> 00:19:13.903 position:50% align:center
Dying is the same.

00:19:13.987 --> 00:19:15.238 position:50% align:center
Killing your own beautiful body

00:19:15.321 --> 00:19:17.365 position:50% align:center
is another kind
of metamorphosis.

00:19:17.449 --> 00:19:20.035 position:50% align:center
