to resist aging are both comedy.

00:19:20.118 --> 00:19:22.787 position:50% align:center
One of them has
to be the real one.

00:19:22.871 --> 00:19:23.496 position:50% align:center
Who is it?

00:19:23.580 --> 00:19:25.957 position:50% align:center
[CURLS A]
Who?

00:19:26.041 --> 00:19:27.375 position:50% align:center
Who?

00:19:28.835 --> 00:19:30.170 position:50% align:center
Who?

00:19:41.848 --> 00:19:44.684 position:50% align:center
Guess I'm gonna have
to blow your mind, too.

00:19:54.486 --> 00:19:56.154 position:50% align:center
[AOI]
How did you...?

00:19:56.237 --> 00:19:59.657 position:50% align:center
