ever call you pretty again.

00:20:14.381 --> 00:20:16.257 position:50% align:center
[NEIRU]
"Why don't I die, too?"

00:20:16.341 --> 00:20:18.218 position:50% align:center
Huh.

00:20:18.301 --> 00:20:22.847 position:50% align:center
"Temptation of death,"
indeed, but I resisted.

00:20:59.009 --> 00:21:00.051 position:50% align:center
Well done.

00:21:00.135 --> 00:21:02.303 position:50% align:center
Teenage rebellion.

00:21:02.387 --> 00:21:05.223 position:50% align:center
They'll want to go
if we say not to.

00:21:05.306 --> 00:21:06.391 position:50% align:center
Somewhere, they
know that rebelling

00:21:06.474 --> 00:21:09.561 position:50% align:center
helps build their
individual identities.

